          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Meanwhile, combine the <strong>Greek-style fat-free yoghurt</strong> with the juice of 1/2<span class=\"text-danger\"> [1]</span> <strong>lemon</strong> and the remaining <strong>chopped mint</strong></p>\r\n<p>Season with a pinch of <strong>salt</strong>&nbsp;&ndash; this is your <strong>minty yoghurt dressing&nbsp;</strong></p>",
      "order": 5,
      "media": {
        "images": [
